	Jolie for Armani    
	 London, July 9: David Beckham and Angelina Jolie are being lined up to appear in a Giorgio Armani advertisement together, reports The Daily Telegraph.       
	It comes after Jolie was reportedly named as the new face of an Armani fragrance. The fashion house is rumoured to have signed the actress two weeks ago after a three-year negotiation. The latest photos were taken by celebrated photography duo Mert Alas and Marcus Piggott.                                                                                                                                                                        
